Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.45,0:01:40.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seeds rooted in the flesh and blood of our ancestors.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.37,0:01:43.99,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Reach out with green, green leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.25,0:01:47.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bear heavy, heavy fruit.
